Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:01:01.66,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Yomigaeru GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:08.00,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,You must seize the power!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:08.00,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kimi yo tsukame
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:14.97,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Fly toward the galaxy, Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:14.97,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Ginga e mukatte tobeyo GANDAMU
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kidou senshi GANDAMU! GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.47,0:01:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The Earth Federation has decided to launch\Nits attack on the special mining base...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.37,0:01:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,...protected by M'Quve's forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.44,0:01:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the start of Operation Odessa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.89,0:01:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,General Revil has sent\Nall of his forces against M'Quve.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.04,0:02:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Although the White Base has\Nreturned to the front lines...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.11,0:02:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,...it was at the cost of many lives\Nincluding Lt. Matilda.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.95,0:02:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The Battle of Odessa
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.15,0:02:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Please make the bare minimum of repairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.60,0:02:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The operation has already started!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.60,0:02:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Just have it ready so I can get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.11,0:02:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, I know! Don't yell!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.86,0:02:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Give him a break. He's a bit edgy\Nafter the loss of Lieutenant Matilda.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.61,0:02:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the same goes for me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.11,0:03:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Matilda...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.05,0:03:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- Amuro!\N- Uh... yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.88,0:03:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't be preoccupied, Amuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.05,0:03:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been ordered to launch. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.23,0:03:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.87,0:03:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.09,0:03:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We're scouting the White Base's route...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.07,0:03:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,...while also getting me used to this thing.\NYou'll help me, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.80,0:03:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.29,0:03:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The G-Armor's taking off!\NStep back now, Fraw Bow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.19,0:03:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro. I'm going to use these Gundam\Npower-up parts that Ms. Matilda brought us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.60,0:03:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to do some practice runs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.72,0:03:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead, Ms. Sayla.\NPlease do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.42,0:04:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm sorry, Mr. Bright.\N- Try to be more careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.68,0:04:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.05,0:04:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to do anything.\NJust let me know if you get an SOS.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.29,0:04:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I understand, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.81,0:04:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fried Chicken, deployment complete!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.09,0:04:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Air Forces are running slow.\i\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.38,0:04:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We need them to send another Dobday!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.72,0:04:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Borscht team from M'Quve's forces,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.06,0:04:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Spirit of Mash...\NMay you soar into space...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.46,0:04:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,...and drift in eternal happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm well aware these soldiers\Nwere recommended by Lady Kycilia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.33,0:04:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But how long are they going to waste\Ntime and energy like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.98,0:04:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Gaia. Ortega. The operation has begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.79,0:04:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We know that already!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.55,0:05:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have our revenge, no need to nag us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.99,0:05:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not a revenge mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.64,0:05:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Take out the Trojan Horse that's threatening\Nus from behind. That's the plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.87,0:05:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.31,0:05:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ortega! We're heading out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.81,0:05:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be approaching\Nthe enemy soon, Ms. Sayla.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.34,0:05:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.64,0:05:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger! Let me try the touch-and-go\None more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We're receiving a message through\Ncode modulation circuit, alpha-gain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.20,0:05:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's General Revil.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.40,0:06:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What? From General Revil?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.97,0:06:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,"At 0630 hours, the White Base is to\Nattack M'Quve's base from the rear."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.74,0:06:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Contact the G-Armor, Fraw Bow,\Nand tell them to return to the White Base...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.17,0:06:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...using cross cycle W. F.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.94,0:06:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes... sir. W. F?\N- Mm-hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.53,0:06:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you really do it properly?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.44,0:06:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I can. You just keep quiet now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.50,0:06:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy's front line is this close?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.55,0:06:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they notice us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.20,0:06:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Please lower our altitude now, Ms. Sayla!\NThey may have spotted us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.76,0:06:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Roger!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.02,0:06:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like a propeller-driven plane.\NI'm not that certain...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.09,0:06:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...but I don't think it's one of Zeon's planes.\N- I'll check.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.96,0:06:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.36,0:06:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A Dragonfly?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.41,0:07:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A small ferry plane used by the Federation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.47,0:07:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did it just come out of a Zeon base?\NAnd how come it wasn't shot down?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.40,0:07:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.79,0:07:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a message from the White Base...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,"Return to ship immediately."\NWhat should we do, Amuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you curious, Ms. Sayla?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.90,0:07:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes... Shall we check it out?\N- All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.72,0:07:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, Ms. Matilda did say...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...the Zeons seemed to know\Nevery move her Medea would make.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.19,0:07:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A spy? It's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.88,0:07:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But if the Medeas were shot down\Nbecause of a spy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.43,0:07:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,...we need to reveal the truth\Nbefore we begin the operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.66,0:07:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Bright! Enemy machines approaching\Nfrom one o'clock, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!\NHeaded straight for us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. But they couldn't have\Ndetected us at this altitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.67,0:07:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There's our proof that we have a spy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.50,0:07:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare for anti-air combat.\NGuntank, Guncannon, prepare to sortie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.62,0:08:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, hold on a moment! operation's schedule?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.43,0:08:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy isn't going to wait\Nuntil it's convenient for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.25,0:08:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Don't waste your ammo.\N- Yeah, okay.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Amuro. The Dragonfly has landed\Non the Federation's Big Tray.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.48,0:08:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Sayla! Wait for me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.93,0:08:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Identify yourself! Name and assignment!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.51,0:08:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Gundam of the White Base!\NMy name is Amuro Ray!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.60,0:08:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Gundam? This thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.06,0:09:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, I need you to tell me\Nwhere I can find the pilot...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.98,0:09:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...of the Dragonfly that just landed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.68,0:09:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean Judock's ferry plane?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.53,0:09:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He's ordered you to betray your own forces\Nas soon as the operation begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.99,0:09:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,M'Quve is a rather restless man, isn't he.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.18,0:09:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Since M'Quve knows you won't be attacking...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.12,0:09:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...he has also ordered his main forces\Nto focus on General Revil.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.13,0:09:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.65,0:09:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- What is it?\N- Sir! We've caught a suspicious person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.78,0:09:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Suspicious...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.36,0:09:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- What do you want?\N- Can we talk alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.93,0:09:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.52,0:09:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You may all leave the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.80,0:09:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.26,0:09:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Judock.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.38,0:09:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Depending on what's discussed in that room,\Nwe might need to interrogate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.89,0:10:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This picture was taken by an official\Nmilitary data-processing camera...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.04,0:10:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...and can be used as evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.52,0:10:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.23,0:10:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to tell me that\Nwe have a spy aboard the Big Tray?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.59,0:10:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. If we enlarge the negative,\Nwe should be able to verify the pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.16,0:10:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You're suggesting that Judock is this spy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.86,0:10:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.32,0:10:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's capital punishment.\NFor Judock...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...and for you, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.38,0:10:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.11,0:10:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody will ask questions\Nif a single person is killed. And besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.53,0:10:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a general.\NNobody will listen to a child like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.21,0:10:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I thought it was impossible,\Nbut... It's you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.36,0:10:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.77,0:10:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of people like you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.02,0:10:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could say I'd spare your life\Nin exchange for the negative...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.23,0:11:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.68,0:11:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro... Great work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.19,0:11:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We have this whole conversation on video.\NIt's more than enough evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.10,0:11:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.60,0:11:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.01,0:11:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You will remain in the brig\Nuntil the operation is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.69,0:11:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to say you had your reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.59,0:11:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But... you're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.73,0:11:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of people like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.89,0:11:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...dozens of people\Nhave died for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.19,0:11:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you even realize that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.77,0:11:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of people like you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.78,0:11:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Son...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.08,0:11:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's leave the rest for the court martial.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.96,0:11:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.34,0:11:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The White Base seems to\Nbe engaged in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I suggest you return at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.99,0:11:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.64,0:11:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.96,0:11:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Our forces will begin the attack{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.29,0:12:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Big Tray, maximum speed!eoff!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.69,0:12:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro. We're taking off. Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.28,0:12:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Roger!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.69,0:12:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.69,0:12:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The battle of Odessa has begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.37,0:12:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Both M'Quve's and Revil's forces...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.64,0:12:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...are headed straight for each other,\Ndeploying their maximum resources.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.11,0:12:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And the White Base is no exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.96,0:13:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.68,0:13:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato! The Guntank won't stand a chance\Nagainst these guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.16,0:13:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Retreat, retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.48,0:13:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.24,0:13:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hands off this one, Dopps!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.36,0:13:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Just focus on downing the Trojan Horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.04,0:13:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and bring in the Guntank!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.95,0:13:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep the mobile suits away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.59,0:13:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro! I hope you'll be back real soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.52,0:13:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Armor is returning,\Nfrom one o'clock, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.38,0:14:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! Prepare to launch the beam rifle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.69,0:14:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro! I can see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.03,0:14:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How's the battle going?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.89,0:14:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.42,0:14:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The Guntank has returned.\NA caterpillar tread was smashed...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.29,0:14:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So Mr. Kai's Guncannon is out there alone.\NHe's in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.28,0:14:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay. Just stay calm and tell mee. Got It?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.19,0:14:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.24,0:14:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll be okay, 'cause I'm with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.91,0:14:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I have you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.56,0:14:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.23,0:14:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, I'm out of shells.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.43,0:14:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's that white mobile suit?\NThe one that killed Mash!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.17,0:14:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the mobile suits\Nfrom last night, Amuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.65,0:14:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be tough to defeat them\Nwithout the Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.59,0:15:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- Wanna convert?\N- White Base, can you hang on for 20 secs?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.68,0:15:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Bright! Amuro's asking for 20 seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.62,0:15:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got no choice. Tell Kai to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.69,0:15:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for Mash!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.61,0:15:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Retreat behind the mountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.47,0:15:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.70,0:15:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Where does that bomber think it's going?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.89,0:15:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Separating G-Armor parts.\NPattern G!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.17,0:15:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Pattern G, acknowledged. Go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.32,0:15:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,4... 3... 2...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.30,0:15:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,...1... 0.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.81,0:15:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The one that got Mash appeared\Nwhen that bomber came out. That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.78,0:16:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That mobile suit...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.83,0:16:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Sayla!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.40,0:16:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.43,0:16:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming in for a landing, White Base.\NAll clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.45,0:16:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Okay. Any damage?\N- A bit along the front.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.18,0:16:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.25,0:16:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll replace it with Hayato's Core Fighter.\NPlease land on the port-side deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.78,0:16:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Aligning laser axis.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.95,0:16:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Once it's in the hangar, we'll remove\Nthe front and attach Hayato's Core Fighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.46,0:16:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger! Docking release, set.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.53,0:16:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Please hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.35,0:17:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato! You'd better not crash it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Does anybody ever take off\Nhoping to crash their fighter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.36,0:17:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Launching!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.40,0:17:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The first line to be broken was where\NM'Quve's forces were spread thin...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.10,0:17:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...counting on General Elran's betrayal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.40,0:17:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, the two Dom mobile suits...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.61,0:17:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,...were caught up with their battle against\NGundam, and unable to join the front line.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.07,0:17:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,As a result, the Zeon forces lacked\Nenough strength to stop the Federation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.39,0:17:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,However, even at this critical moment,\NM'Quve still had a last resort.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.15,0:17:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This is addressed to General Revil,\Ncommander of Operation Odessa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.52,0:17:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I am M'Quve.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.53,0:17:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do not withdraw your forces...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.81,0:18:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...we are prepared to use hydrogen bombs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.19,0:18:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this goes against the Antarctic Treaty\Nprohibiting the use of nuclear weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.45,0:18:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But we don't want to lose, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.59,0:18:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It is said that General Revil\Ndid not say a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.40,0:18:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He simply waved his hand\Nto indicate that his forces were to proceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.12,0:18:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Using those same tactics again?\NDon't take us for fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.89,0:19:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Ortega... He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.39,0:19:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'll get you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.35,0:19:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Amuro! Do you read me?drogen bomb!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.07,0:19:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A hydrogen bomb?! But that's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.96,0:19:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, It Is. The enemy Is usingd.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.37,0:19:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We have 30 secondslaunch.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.86,0:19:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about the mobile suit.\NOur priority is to destroy the missile!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.73,0:19:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But...! There's no way I can do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.35,0:19:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sending you some data.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.50,0:19:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The red area Is the trigger mechanism.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.40,0:19:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You just need to cute.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.80,0:19:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But can such a crude diagram...\Nreally be of any use?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.52,0:19:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not sure.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.10,0:19:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was released when the Antarctic Treaty{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.81,0:19:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Incoming!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.83,0:19:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's a real hydrogen bomb,\Nwe'll all be destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.62,0:20:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to do it, Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.36,0:20:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- If it's real?\N- That's right!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.96,0:20:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's real...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.52,0:20:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Hayato! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.97,0:20:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Doms can perform stunts like yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.64,0:20:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! You mean Revil's forces\Nhaven't stopped their advance?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.67,0:20:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. They're very close to breaking through\Nour final line of defense, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.11,0:20:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Those fools...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.85,0:20:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an enemy mobile suit\Nbattling with a Dom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.35,0:20:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So the Federation Forces have taken\Ndrastic measures against us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.02,0:20:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll give them what they asked for.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.11,0:20:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But sir, it's too late to...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.49,0:20:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This is how the game is played.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.65,0:20:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The Federation has blatantly\Nignored our demands
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.67,0:20:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So they must now\Nface the consequences...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.33,0:20:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Launch the missile!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.32,0:21:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato! Full power!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.72,0:21:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Roger that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.62,0:21:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Can... I do it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.08,0:21:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Mash...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.57,0:21:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ortega...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.98,0:21:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.73,0:22:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Operation Odessa has ended in victory\Nfor the Federation Forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.51,0:22:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,However, M'Quve has escaped...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.34,0:22:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...on the Zanzibar warship that had\Nbrought the Black Tri-Stars to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.37,0:22:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This battle isn't the end of the war...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.23,0:22:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.94,0:22:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,With the amount of mineral\Nresources we've sent...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.14,0:22:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...Zeon can fight for another 10 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.11,0:23:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The young crew of the White Base...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.51,0:23:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...are introduced to General Revil\Non friendly terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.96,0:23:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mad Angler squadron deploys\Nthe amphibious mobile suit Gogg.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.28,0:23:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to crush the Trojan Horse\Nand destroy the Gundam...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.75,0:23:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The Goggs attack with extraordinary tactics\Nas they threaten the White Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.22,0:23:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the commander of the Mad Angler\Nsquadron is none other than...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.36,0:23:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam. Next episode...\NChar Returns.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.97,0:23:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Char Returns
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.22,0:23:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be able to survive?
